title: Battleground.S01E03.Hold.the.Whipped.Cream.WEBRip.XviD-Eclipse
description:
ABOUT THE SHOW
Battleground is a documentary-style drama series created by JD Walsh that chronicles the inner workings of a Democratic Party primary campaign for a U.S. Senate seat in Wisconsin. Led by campaign manager Chris "Tak" Davis, the team battles against corrupt politicians and staff infighting while campaigning for a distant third-place candidate. The show marks hulu's first foray into original scripted programming.


IN THE THIRD EPISODE
The Samuels campaign has until the end of the day to raise enough money to continue in the race. Jordan prepares for his stand-up comedy debut.

Cheers to Eclipse for releasing this show.
